relevant_findings.general: Alert, oriented to name, place and situation. Fatigued appearing but comfortable, no acute signs of distress.
relevant_findings.eyes: Pupils equal and reactive, sclerae anicteric.
relevant_findings.ent: Normocephalic, atraumatic, oropharynx clear, dry mucous membranes.
relevant_findings.cardiovascular: S1S2, regular rate and rhythm, systolic ejection murmur, no rubs or gallops.
relevant_findings.respiratory: Good air movement bilaterally, no rhonchi or wheezing. No accessory muscle use.
relevant_findings.abdominal: Soft, tender to palpation in the epigastric and right upper quadrant, non-distended, positive bowel sounds.
relevant_findings.extremities: No lower leg edema, no clubbing or cyanosis.
relevant_findings.neurological: Cranial nerves grossly intact, muscle strength normal in all major muscle groups, sensation to light touch intact, non-focal.
